NDP foreign affairs

00:25:04.100 --> 00:25:06.450
critic who lost a seat
recently in the election.

00:25:06.450 --> 00:25:10.620
But he also had taken
steps around this issue.

00:25:10.620 --> 00:25:14.820
And again, I don't want to--
the answers are not simple.

00:25:14.820 --> 00:25:17.630
It does need a
development approach.

00:25:17.630 --> 00:25:19.900
It needs a governance approach.

00:25:19.900 --> 00:25:22.600
It needs a diplomatic approach.

00:25:22.600 --> 00:25:25.240
But all of that
can happen as long

00:25:25.240 --> 00:25:28.560
as there is acknowledgement from
the industry and a willingness

00:25:28.560 --> 00:25:30.850
to lead change.

00:25:30.850 --> 00:25:32.862
And if we can even
start there and begin

00:25:32.862 --> 00:25:34.070
to have those conversations--

00:25:34.070 --> 00:25:35.735
ADAM GREEN: Just recognize
that we have a problem.

00:25:35.735 --> 00:25:36.800
SAMANTHA NUTT: Recognize
we have a problem,

00:25:36.800 --> 00:25:38.970
and that's exactly what
happened with conflict diamonds.

00:25:38.970 --> 00:25:40.870
For a while, the industry was
like, there isn't a problem.

00:25:40.870 --> 00:25:41.786
There isn't a problem.

00:25:41.786 --> 00:25:44.460
And they ran from it and
they lobbied against it.

00:25:44.460 --> 00:25:46.550
And then finally, they
said, we do have a problem.

00:25:46.550 --> 00:25:48.780
The Kimberly Process
is imperfect.

00:25:48.780 --> 00:25:50.530
The fact that Zimbabwean
diamonds were not

00:25:50.530 --> 00:25:54.350
considered conflict diamonds
is a huge gaping hole

00:25:54.350 --> 00:25:55.630
in that process.

00:25:55.630 --> 00:25:57.550
But it's a step in
the right direction.

00:25:57.550 --> 00:26:00.110
And even if it's
imperfect to start,

00:26:00.110 --> 00:26:01.569
at least we're
making that effort.

00:26:01.569 --> 00:26:02.860
ADAM GREEN: Yeah, do something.

00:26:02.860 --> 00:26:03.660
Something is better
than nothing.

00:26:03.660 --> 00:26:05.610
SAMANTHA NUTT: Something is
usually better than nothing.

00:26:05.610 --> 00:26:06.190
ADAM GREEN: Usually.

00:26:06.190 --> 00:26:07.148
SAMANTHA NUTT: Usually.

