00:43:17.329 --> 00:43:18.870
that people may have
forgotten about,

00:43:18.870 --> 00:43:22.320
that they're no longer
in the headlines.

00:43:22.320 --> 00:43:23.800
Write those strongly
worded letters

00:43:23.800 --> 00:43:25.860
to your members of parliament.

00:43:25.860 --> 00:43:27.240
Try to make that difference.

00:43:27.240 --> 00:43:31.800
And we have some books,
